Knowler reported no conflicts of interest.


185. Prevalence and Incidence of Type 1 Diabetes Among Children and Adults in the
 United States and Comparison With Non-U.S. Countries.

Imperatore G(1), Mayer-Davis EJ(2), Orchard TJ(3), Zhong VW(4).

