Social and economic cost of eating disorders in the United States: Evidence to 
inform policy action.

Streatfeild J(1), Hickson J(1), Austin SB(2)(3)(4)(5), Hutcheson R(5)(6), Kandel 
JS(7), Lampert JG(8)(9), Myers EM(10), Richmond TK(2)(3)(5), Samnaliev 
M(2)(3)(5), Velasquez K(11), Weissman RS(12), Pezzullo L(1).
